**Summary:** Documents the CCPA Data Subject Access Request (DSAR) API for retrieving all user data through an asynchronous 3-step process (POST request → polling GET status → downloading gzipped JSON files), with specific rate limits of 14.4K cost/hour, 3-day SLA, and support for userId/amplitudeId queries.

